<li><a href="http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/1506" rel="bookmark" title="Tumblr，点点，推他 |下厨房 | sinaapp">Tumblr，点点，推他 |下厨房 | sinaapp </a><hr /></li>
<li><a href="http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/1453" rel="bookmark" title="Google Guitar Doodle">Google Guitar Doodle </a><hr /></li>
</ol></p>
</div>
